title: LIVE from Oxonmoot
description:
We'll be LIVE from the Lamb & Flag pub in Oxford, UK during the Tolkien Society's annual Tolkien conference: Oxonmoot!  Joining me will be Brian Sibley, with more guests to come!

#oxonmoot #tolkien #oxford

title: 🔴NEWS: War of the Rohirrim DELAYED, Return to Moria Gameplay Revealed & More!
description:
For the first time in a while, we got news from two separate Middle-earth projects.  We'll chat about War of the Rohirrim being delayed until December 2024 and check out some of the gameplay from the new Return to Moria game!

#waroftherohirrim #returntomoria #lordoftherings
